      "content": "yeah... it's like i'm just waiting for something to happen. i look at my life and i don't see a future, i just see more of this. people say things get better but they're lying. it just gets louder. i feel like i'm just taking up space for no reason. if i wasn't here, the bullying would stop, the noise would stop, and everyone could just move on without having to deal with me. it feels like the only way to actually find some peace is to just not be around anymore.",
